        Quick start
        ===========
        
        Install from PyPI::
        
            $ pip install variadic
        
        Import:
        
        >>> from variadic import variadic
        
        Define a function:
        
        >>> @variadic(int)
        ... def f(*args):
        ...   return args
        >>> f(1, 2, [3, 4], xrange(5, 8))
        (1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7)
        
